### Reachly API — HTTP examples (works with VS Code REST Client extension)

@base = http://localhost:3000/api
@token = PASTE_YOUR_JWT_HERE

### Health check
GET http://localhost:3000/health

### Register as influencer
POST {{base}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "sana@reachly.pk",
  "password": "testpass123",
  "name": "Sana Amjad",
  "role": "influencer",
  "handle": "sanaamjad"
}

### Login
POST {{base}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "sana@reachly.pk",
  "password": "testpass123"
}

### Get current user
GET {{base}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### List all influencers
GET {{base}}/influencers

### Get influencer profile + session types
GET {{base}}/influencers/sanaamjad

### Get availability for a date
GET {{base}}/influencers/sanaamjad/availability?date=2026-04-07

### Create a session type (influencer token)
POST {{base}}/sessions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Quick Chat",
  "description": "Ask me anything.",
  "duration_minutes": 20,
  "price_pkr": 2500
}

### Create a booking (follower token)
POST {{base}}/bookings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "session_type_id": "PASTE_SESSION_TYPE_UUID",
  "influencer_id": "PASTE_INFLUENCER_UUID",
  "scheduled_at": "2026-04-07T11:30:00+05:00",
  "payment_method": "jazzcash",
  "note": "Would love to discuss growing my Instagram!"
}

### Get my bookings
GET {{base}}/bookings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Confirm a booking (influencer token)
PATCH {{base}}/bookings/PASTE_BOOKING_UUID/confirm
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Cancel a booking
PATCH {{base}}/bookings/PASTE_BOOKING_UUID/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get influencer dashboard
GET {{base}}/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
